{"name":"江雪左文字","nameCn":"江雪左文字","cover":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/crt/m/a3/2c/29180_crt_0tLQj.jpg","info":"<li><span>简体中文名: </span>江雪左文字</li><li><span>别名: </span>太刀</li><li><span style=\"visibility:hidden;\">别名: </span>左文字</li><li><span style=\"visibility:hidden;\">别名: </span>こうせつさもんじ</li><li><span style=\"visibility:hidden;\">别名: </span>Kousetsusamonji</li><li><span>性别: </span>男</li><li><span>绘师: </span>鈴木次郎</li>","detail":"･･････江雪左文字と申します。板部岡江雪斎の佩刀だったが故にこう名付けられました。<br />･･････刀は、使われぬほうが良いのです。<br />抜かれる前、振るわれぬように、和睦に勤める。それが大事なのではないでしょうか。<br /><br />江雪左文字（こうせつさもんじ）とは、刀工左文字の作による日本刀。左文字の在銘刀としては唯一の作品。<br />北条家支流田中内膳泰行の子後北条氏家臣板部岡江雪斎から豊臣秀吉に献上され、その後徳川家康を経て紀州徳川家に伝わった。現在は国宝指定を受けている。","jobs":[{"href":"/subject/113559","name":"刀剣乱舞-ONLINE-","nameCn":"刀剑乱舞-ONLINE-","cover":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/cover/g/d4/3a/113559_d0dYu.jpg","staff":"主角","cast":"佐藤拓也","castHref":"/person/5151","castTag":"CV","castCover":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/crt/s/4f/15/5151_prsn_b2sI9.jpg","type":4},{"href":"/subject/226653","name":"『刀剣乱舞-花丸-』歌詠全集","nameCn":"","cover":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/cover/g/46/3c/226653_4kI42.jpg","staff":"主角","cast":"","castHref":"","castTag":"","castCover":"","type":3},{"href":"/subject/237448","name":"続『刀剣乱舞-花丸-』歌詠集 其の六","nameCn":"","cover":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/cover/g/0f/80/237448_Q12ZL.jpg","staff":"主角","cast":"","castHref":"","castTag":"","castCover":"","type":3},{"href":"/subject/175525","name":"刀剣乱舞-花丸-","nameCn":"刀剑乱舞-花丸-","cover":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/cover/g/0b/fc/175525_0NtRQ.jpg","staff":"配角","cast":"佐藤拓也","castHref":"/person/5151","castTag":"CV","castCover":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/crt/s/4f/15/5151_prsn_b2sI9.jpg","type":2},{"href":"/subject/208370","name":"続『刀剣乱舞-花丸-』","nameCn":"续「刀剑乱舞-花丸-」","cover":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/cover/g/e6/3e/208370_2LT6G.jpg","staff":"配角","cast":"佐藤拓也","castHref":"/person/5151","castTag":"CV","castCover":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/crt/s/4f/15/5151_prsn_b2sI9.jpg","type":2}]}